        <mxCell id="title" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=14;spacingLeft=10;" value="&lt;b&gt;Dual-Cluster Deployment — hall1 + hall2&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;4 pods (2 per hall). Shared TREP load balancer (HA pair). Shared Enterprise Redis. 1 DACS user × 2 concurrent sessions." vertex="1">
